# Assets folder

## To add your profile photo:

1. Save your photo as `profile.jpg` in this folder.
   - Recommended size: **600×600 px** (square).
   - JPG or PNG works (if PNG, also rename to `profile.png` and update the `<img src>` in `index.html`).
2. The image will appear automatically in the hero card.
3. If no photo is found, the site shows a stylish **DS** initials fallback (no broken icon).

## To add your downloadable CV:

1. Save your CV as `Dev_Sajal_CV.pdf` in this folder.
2. The “Download CV” button in the header will serve it.

## Folder structure expected on GitHub Pages:

```
portfolio/
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── assets/
    ├── profile.jpg          (your photo)
    └── Dev_Sajal_CV.pdf     (your CV)
```

